
<section class="row">
    @* Heading section *@
    
    <section class="mt-3">
        <div class="col-6 mx-auto text-center">
            <h1 class="text-primary fw-bold text-decoration-underline">The Peregrine's nest.</h1>
            <h2 class="text-light">Taste flavours you never knew existed.</h2>
        </div>
    </section>

    @* Carousel images section *@

    <div class="mt-3">
        <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img src="~/Images/ClientHomePage/Carousel/Carousel1.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="An image of the inside of a store at night.">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="~/Images/ClientHomePage/Carousel/Carousel2.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="An image of the inside of a store during the day.">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="~/Images/ClientHomePage/Carousel/Carousel3.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="An image of the outside of a store, showing the shop front.">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="~/Images/ClientHomePage/Carousel/Carousel4.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="A image of the inside of the store, on a rainy night.">
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
            </button>
            <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    @* Restaurant story section *@
    <section class="mt-5">
        <h2 class="text-center text-decoration-underline">Our story...</h2>
        <div class="text-light test-justify mt-4">
            <p>
                In the heart of a bustling city, nestled among the chaotic streets and vibrant culture,
                stood a modest yet promising establishment: "The Peregrine's nest." Its origins were humble,
                born from the passion and culinary prowess of a young chef named Antonio Savoria.
                With a vision to blend traditional flavors with innovative techniques,
                Antonio opened his restaurant with a handful of family recipes and a dream to create an unforgettable dining experience.
            </p>
            <p>
                As time passed, "The Peregrine's nest" became a beacon of gastronomic delight, drawing food enthusiasts from far and wide.
                One fateful evening, inspired by the fragrant spices of his grandmother's kitchen, Antonio crafted his masterpiece: "The Peregrine's Signature Dish."
                This exquisite creation, a symphony of tender lamb, aromatic herbs, and secret spices, soon became the talk of the town.
                Word spread like wildfire, and soon, diners traveled from across the globe to savor this culinary marvel.
            </p>
            <p>
                But it wasn't just one dish that put "The Peregrine's nest" on the map; it was a series of serendipitous moments and creative experiments.
                From a chance encounter with a rare ingredient to a nostalgic childhood memory, each dish on the menu had its own captivating story.
                Whether it was the succulent seafood stew inspired by Antonio's seaside adventures or the decadent chocolate dessert born from a happy accident in the kitchen,
                every bite at "The Peregrine's nest" told a tale of passion, innovation, and the relentless pursuit of culinary perfection.
                And so, the legacy of this remarkable restaurant continued to grow, leaving an indelible mark on the world of fine dining.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>


